OL,3,CCoventry City supporters urged to clap
OL,4,Cfor fan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FFootball fans at the FA Cup semi-final
OL,7,Fmatch between and Manchester United
OL,8,Fare being encouraged to clap in the
OL,9,F21st minute for a Coventry City
OL,10,Fsupporter who is stuck in hospital on
OL,11,Fan urgent waiting list for a heart
OL,12,Ftransplant.
OL,14,FLouis O'Brien-Smith, from , has
OL,15,Fdilated cardiomyopathy, which is
OL,16,Fbelieved to be caused by chemotherapy
OL,17,Fhe underwent for leukaemia. Louis had
OL,18,Fcancer twice as a child.
