OL,3,CCoventry City supporters urged to clap
OL,4,Cfor fan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FNow 21, Louis has been stuck in a
OL,7,Fhospital room for weeks, not knowing
OL,8,Fwhen he is going to be able to leave,
OL,9,Fand not allowed to leave until he has
OL,10,Fa new heart.
OL,12,FLast week, doctors finally announced
OL,13,Fthe news that Louis was going to have
OL,14,Fa new heart.
OL,16,FHowever, after prepping Louis for a
OL,17,Fheart replacement operation, it was
OL,18,Fcancelled at the last minute as the
OL,19,Freplacement heart was not responding
OL,20,Fproperly.
