OL,3,CCoventry City supporters urged to clap
OL,4,Cfor fan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FMum Chantelle Spiers told ITV Central:
OL,7,F"For me I don't want my little hero to
OL,8,Ffeel forgotten while he waits within
OL,9,Fthe hospital walls". She added, "the
OL,10,Ffuture is uncertain and all he can do
OL,11,Fis wait and hold on to hope that a
OL,12,Fheart will become available."
OL,14,F"My son has battled all of his life.
OL,15,FIt feels so unfair and so, so cruel.
OL,16,FThe situation right now feels so scary
OL,17,Fand I cannot bare the thought of
OL,18,Flosing him. If I can rally around
OL,19,Fsupport now to show Louis how we are
OL,20,Fall behind him then that is what I
OL,21,Fshall do!".
