OL,4,Cfor fan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FDespite being stuck in isolation in a
OL,7,Fhotel room, Louis' mum is keen to show
OL,8,Fhim that he isn't alone.
OL,10,F"For the supporters to clap for him on
OL,11,Fthe 21st minute will show him as he
OL,12,Fwatches away from home that he isn't
OL,13,Fforgotten".
OL,15,F"To know that half of the city, his
OL,16,Fhome town are thinking of him and
OL,17,Facknowledging him means the world!".
