OL,6,FThe hope and end goal for Louis and
OL,7,Fhis Mum Chantelle is to raise
OL,8,Fawareness of his condition and of
OL,9,Forgan donation.
OL,11,FThey've had the support of singer and
OL,12,Frapper YoungBloodRap, who produced a
OL,13,Fsong called 'Mr High (Louis Tribute)'
OL,14,Fthat tells Louis' story and mentions
OL,15,Fthe importance of donors.
