OL,3,CCoventry City supporters urged to clap
OL,4,Cfor fan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FAnd Louis has even amounted a social
OL,7,Fmedia account following of over
OL,8,F60,000, much to the amazement of his
OL,9,FMum. She says that: "In the words of
OL,10,Fhis TikTok followers- he's waiting for
OL,11,Fa heart fit for a king!".
OL,13,FFrom a young age, Louis has always
OL,14,Fstruggled with his health. He had
OL,15,Fmeningitis at 11 weeks old and at 18
OL,16,Fmonths was diagnosed with acute
OL,17,Fmyeloid leukaemia, a rare and
OL,18,Faggressive form of cancer and he
OL,19,Fovercame it twice.
