OL,6,FHowever Louis went on to have
OL,7,Fcomplications from chemotherapy
OL,8,Fincluding damage to his bones, legs,
OL,9,Ftibia and hips, but also to his heart,
OL,10,Fleading to him being put on an urgent
OL,11,Fheart transplant waiting list.
OL,13,FHis Mum even says that he's spent so
OL,14,Flong in and out of hospital treatment
OL,15,Fin Birmingham, that he's got a bit of
OL,16,Fa Brummie accent.
