OL,3,CCoventry City supporters urged to clap
OL,4,Cfor fan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FHe struggles to walk, and his main
OL,7,Fambition was to just walk his dog
OL,8,Fbefore last Christmas, but because of
OL,9,Fthe severity of his multiple health
OL,10,Fconditions, he was not able to.
OL,12,FBut that won't stop him from carrying
OL,13,Fon fighting. His Mum said: "I don't
OL,14,Fwant to wake up for the worst to
OL,15,Fhappen and wish I could have done
OL,16,Fmore. Louis is 21 now, he's living
OL,17,Fbreathing and fighting now".
OL,19,F"From his hospital bed he raises the
OL,20,Fimportance and awareness of the need
OL,21,Ffor organ donation".
